FBIS4-58726 "drnes088_a_94003" FBIS-NES-94-088 Daily Report 5 May 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Country Urges Yemeni Factions To End Fighting Country Urges Yemeni Factions To End Fighting LD0505183594 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 5 May 94 LD0505183594 Algiers Radio Algiers Network Arabic BFN [Text] In its capacity as Arab Maghreb Union chairman, Algeria appealed to the brothers in Yemen to put an immediate end to armed confrontation to make room for good efforts, warning of the dangers of this escalation and its dire consequences on civil peace and stability in the region. The Foreign Affairs Ministry spokesman today renewed Algeria's readiness to exert all efforts to contribute toward containing the crisis and giving preference to dialogue among the Yemenis.
